name: .RLIB File Extension
summary: Learn about .RLIB files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: In Linux, you can use the objdump -d command or the Unix archiver (ar) to view an RLIB file's contents. In Windows, macOS, and Linux, you can use rustc (included with Rust) to link an RLIB file to a program while compiling that program.
